{"name":"Barfighter","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"any chaotic","hitDice":"4","armorName":"chain shirt","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"16 (chain shirt, shield)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"76 (9d8 + 36)","speedDesc":"35 ft.","strPoints":"15","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"17","intPoints":"9","wisPoints":"11","chaPoints":"9","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The wolf reaver dwarf can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The wolf reaver dwarf regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the wolf reaver dwarf can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the wolf reaver dwarf can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The wolf reaver dwarf can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the wolf reaver dwarf's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the wolf reaver dwarf's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the wolf reaver dwarf dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Reckless","desc":"At the start of its turn, the [MON] can gain advantage on all melee weapon attack rolls during that turn, but attack rolls against it have advantage until the start of its next turn."}],"actions":[{"name":"Improvised Weapon","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ The [MON] makes a DC 10 strength check. On a failure it deals [STR 1d4] bludgeoning damage. On a success it deals [STR 1d10] bludgeoning damage and the target must make a DC 10 Wisdom save or be stunned until they take damage."},{"name":"Unarmed Strike","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target, two-handed. _Hit:_ [STR 1d4] bludgeoning damage."},{"name":"Dagger","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d4 + 4) piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Tavern Brawler","desc":"The [MON] may attempt a grapple"},{"name":"Unarmed Strike","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [1d4] bludgeoning damage."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}